data.description: UNDER CONSTRUCTION  The Windward L floor plan by Kerley Family Homes This Master on Main plan with its elegant 2 story foyer has a formal Dining Room   Hardwoods in Family, Dining and the lovely Keeping Room  This Keeping room is off the large Gourmet Kitchen with all white cabinetry, quartz counter tops and  gas cook top  The Keeping room has its own stacked stone gas log fireplace.  The coffered ceiling Family room has a gas log, stacked stone fireplace as well  Upstairs has 3 gracious bedrooms plus a Media Room.  All this with a covered patio and a full daylight basement    2 car side entry garage and 3rd car carriage garage. The builder's warranty and installation of the Pestban system are standard. Pictures may be of a finished home with the same floor plan and not of this actual house.
